maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: Sacrebleu, what just happened?
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: Sacrebleu, qu'est-ce qui s'est passé ?

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: Looks like we got transported into the observatory.
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: On dirait que l'on a été transporté dans l'observatoire.
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.note: de: beamen, which would be 'on a été beamé' in bad french

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: [nods]
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: [acquiesce]

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: Why not just open the door?
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: Pourquoi ne pas avoir juste ouvert la porte ?

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: I'm actually wondering about that, too.
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: Je me demandais aussi.

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: Maybe it's to make sure only 5 enter at the same time?
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: Peut-être pour être sûr que les 5 personnes entrent vraiment en même temps ?

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: Well, best to just have a look around, right?
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: Bon, on n'a qu'à observer les environs, non ?

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: Yes, I want my loot!
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: Oui, je veux mon butin !

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: You have conquered even the most daring trials.
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: Vous avez conquis les épreuves les plus audacieuses.

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig:
You, the traveler, 
the envoy of change.
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text:
Vous, le voyageur.
L'émissaire du changement.

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: To seek wisdom of the gods, we built this observatory.
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: Pour trouver la sagesse des dieux, nous avons construit cet observatoire.

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig:
May it be your guiding light in wait
for the message from the sky.
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text:
Laissez-le vous guider par sa lumière
en attendant le message venu du ciel.

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: For your achievements, we grant you the ability to become even stronger.
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text: Pour vos accomplissements nous vous offrons la capacité de devenir plus fort.

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig: CP for all Elements

maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.orig:
Let your every step
form the path of your growth.
maps/autumn/observatory/inner.json/entit.text:
Que chacun de vos pas
dessine le chemin de votre croissance.
